OL,3,CMan charged with murder after woman
OL,4,Cfound to have drowned in Oxfordshire
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith one count of murder after the
OL,8,Fdeath of a woman in Henley-on-Thames
OL,9,Fin Oxfordshire.
OL,11,FNelio Gouveia from Phyllis Court Drive
OL,12,Fhas been remanded in custody and is
OL,13,Fdue to appear at High Wycombe
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court later today (Monday
OL,15,F9 March).
OL,17,FThames Valley Police Officers
OL,18,Fresponded to a call at Phyllis Court
OL,19,FDrive on Friday (6 March) morning
OL,20,Ffollowing the death of a 44-year-old
OL,21,Fwoman from Henley-on-Thames.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
