OL,3,CMan charged with murder after woman
OL,4,Cfound to have drowned in Oxfordshire
OL,6,FA post-mortem carried out over the
OL,7,Fweekend recorded that the cause of
OL,8,Fdeath was drowning.
OL,10,FThames Valley Police have informed the
OL,11,Fwoman's next of kin who are being
OL,12,Fsupported by specially-trained
OL,13,Fofficers.
OL,15,FHowever, the force said that it is not
OL,16,Fyet in a position to release the
OL,17,Fvictim's name.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
