OL,3,CMan charged with murder after woman
OL,4,Cfound to have drowned in Oxfordshire
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Thames Valley
OL,7,FPolice said: "We have liaised with the
OL,8,FCrown Prosecution Service, and this
OL,9,Fevening (8/3) they have authorised a
OL,10,Fcharge in relation to this incident.
OL,12,F"(Nelio Gouveia) has been remanded in
OL,13,Fcustody and will appear at High
OL,14,FWycombe Magistrates court on Monday (9/
OL,15,F3)."
